import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Row, Image, Col, Dropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { TiInfoLarge } from 'react-icons/ti'
import { BsFillCircleFill } from 'react-icons/bs'

class Info_user extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Row className='pl-4 align-items-center'>
                <Col>
                    <BsFillCircleFill className='position-absolute' style={{ margin: '-4px 12px', color: '#f56c6c' }} />
                    <TiInfoLarge size={25} />
                </Col>
                <Col>
                    <Dropdown>
                        <Dropdown.Toggle style={{ backgroundColor: 'transparent', borderColor: 'transparent' }} color='white'>
                            <Image style={{ height: '37px', width: '37px' }} roundedCircle src='https://cdn.viblo.asia/_nuxt/img/0bca52a.png'></Image>
                        </Dropdown.Toggle>

                        <Dropdown.Menu>
                            <Dropdown.Item>  <Card
                                bg='light'
                                style={{ width: '18rem' }}
                                
                            >
                                <Card.Header>Header</Card.Header>
                                <Card.Body>
                                    <Card.Title>{variant} Card Title </Card.Title>
                                    <Card.Text>
                                        Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk
                                        of the card's content.
      </Card.Text>
                                </Card.Body>
                            </Card></Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</Dropdown.Item>
                            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</Dropdown.Item>
                        </Dropdown.Menu>
                    </Dropdown>

                </Col>
            </Row >
        );
    }
}

export default Info_user;
